sub_title: Account Manager at WE ARE Pi | Creativepool Small Agency of the year 2020 |
summary:
A Leader, critical thinker & problem solver fuelled with passion for meaningful creativity. I'm a multilingual senior account manager with vast international experience who fell in love with advertising ever since I stepped into its magical world. 

Having worked 4+ years in the industry allowed me to have both supportive & leading roles in a variety of projects for clients such as Heineken (Desperados, Strongbow), Intersport, Rockstar, Desigual, WeTransfer, IDFA, Winkelstraat.nl and many more. Some of the many highlights of my journey so far include: 

Leading the launch of an Experience Lead Desperados' campaign.
Playing an integral role in an innovation lead NFTee project for Winkelstraat.nl. 
Supporting the production of a documentary for WeTransfer focusing on black female entrepreneurs.
Helping Desigual's brand re-launch by permanently flipping its logo showing that the brand found its crazy again.

Having lived, worked & studied in five different countries made me extremely adaptable to new situations, with the desire to be part of an international environment.
